               <head>Collection of Astronomical works</head>
               
               
               
               <msContents class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85009019" rend="visible">
                  
                  
                  
                  <summary>Astronomical works.</summary>
                  
                  
                  
                  <textLang mainLang="he"/>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="" class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85009019">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="1r" to="11v"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">῾Iyun shivah kokhave lekhet</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">עיון שבעה כוכבי לכת</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName key="viaf.org/viaf/84814786" xml:lang="en">Gherardo, da Cremona</persName>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="he" key="viaf.org/viaf/84814786">גררדוס מסביוניטה</persName>
                     
                     
                     
                     </author>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>A Hebrew translation by Yehudah (Astruc) ben Shemu᾿el Shalom of 'Theorica Planetarium' of Gherardo da Cremona. The name of the scribe, Shabtai ben Mordekhai of Sulmona, is mentioned in the heading, below a diagram showing the signs of the zodiac. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="12r" to="45r"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="en" key="viaf.org/viaf/59118174">Levi ben Gershom</persName>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="he" key="viaf.org/viaf/59118174">לוי בן גרשום</persName>
                     
                     
                     
                     </author>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Luḥot astronomiyim</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">לוחות אסטרונומיים</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>The astronomical tables (folios 20v-45r) follow a short exposition, which begins on folio 14r. </p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>See further Goldstein, B.R., The Astronomical Tables of Levi ben Gerson (New Haven 1974), p. 77.</p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="45v" to="59r"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="en" key="viaf.org/viaf/61397975">Al-Aḥdab, Iṣḥak ben Shlomo</persName>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="he" key="viaf.org/viaf/61397975">חדב, יצחק בן שלמה</persName>
                     
                     
                     
                     </author>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Oraḥ selulah</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">ארח סלולה</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>The astronomical tables occupy folios 48v-59r. There are many comments and notes in the margin. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                     
                     
                     
                     <filiation>Cf. Or 2806. </filiation>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="59v" to="65v"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Luḥot ha-po῾el</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">לוחות הפועל</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="en" key="viaf.org/viaf/43519705">Ben David Bonjorn, Jacob</persName>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="he" key="viaf.org/viaf/43519705">בוניט, יעקב בן דוד בן יום טוב פועל</persName>
                     
                     
                     
                     </author>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>The astronomical tables, with a preceding exposition. Folio 65r and 65v are all that is preserved in the manuscript of the tables themselves. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
               
               
               
               </msContents>
               
               
               
               <physDesc rend="visible">
                  
                  
                  
                  <p>Parchment codex of the 15th century.</p>
                  
                  
                  
                  <objectDesc form="codex">
                     
                     
                     
                     <supportDesc material="perg">
                        
                        
                        
                        <support>Parchment. </support>
                        
                        
                        
                        <extent>65 folios<dimensions type="leaf" unit="mm">
                              
                              
                              
                              <height>215</height>
                              
                              
                              
                              <width>145</width>
                           
                           
                           
