                        </extent>
                        
                        
                        
                        <foliation>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>65 folios (+ 3 unfoliated paper flyleaf at the beginning and at the end). Folio 1 is a paper flyleaf. </p>
                        
                        
                        
                        </foliation>
                        
                        
                        
                        <collation>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Quires of mostly 8 leaves each. </p>
                        
                        
                        
                        </collation>
                        
                        
                        
                        <condition>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Imperfect at the end. </p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>First few and last leaves damaged by damp and mould, with some losses and brittle edges. The damage was repaired, probably before rebinding. </p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Damp entry at corners and edges with tidemarks. </p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Slight dirt entry at head. </p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>A few usage stains.
</p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Binding rubbed at joints. Raised bands. </p>
                        
                        
                        
                        </condition>
                     
                     
                     
                     </supportDesc>
                     
                     
                     
                     <layoutDesc>
                        
                        
                        
                        <layout columns="1" ruledLines="30 43" writtenLines="30 43">
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Uniform layout.</p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Pricking and hard-point ruling is visible.</p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Flesh side and hair side of folios is distinguishable. </p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Some marginal notes. </p>
                        
                        
                        
                        </layout>
                     
                     
                     
                     </layoutDesc>
                  
                  
                  
